*“Fact and Faith: Why Science and Spirituality are not Incompatible,” &quot;BBC Focus&quot;, 5, April 2018
*“The Coronavirus is a Reminder of Something Lost Long Ago,” &quot;The Atlantic&quot;, April 1, 2020
